description:
Collected data from the field experiment Soil Effects of Nors&oslash;k (Tingvoll, Norway), sampled in 2024-2026 by University Kaiserslautern-Landau (RPTU) group of prof. dr. Hermann Jungkunst.&nbsp; 
 File contains more detailed description of the individual parameters in Tab "info". 
 More details on the Soil Effects experiment, see previous entry or    https://doi.org/10.1016/j.dib.2024.110201    
 &nbsp; 
 Still work in progress! File will be updated when data collection is finished

